                                "mergeField": "%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2012pt;%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance%20for%20Disclosure%20410-1%20%3C/strong%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EThe%20training%20can%20refer%20either%20to%20training%20dedicated%20to%20the%20subject%20of%20human%20rights%20or%20to%20a%20human%20rights%20module%20within%20a%20general%20training%20program.%20Training%20can%20cover%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20use%20of%20force,%20inhuman%20or%20degrading%20treatment%20or%20discrimination,%20or%20identification%20and%20registering.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Background%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EThe%20use%20of%20security%20personnel%20can%20play%20an%20essential%20role%20in%20allowing%20an%20organization%20to%20operate%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20productive%20manner,%20and%20can%20contribute%20to%20the%20security%20of%20local%20communities%20and%20populations.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EHowever,%20as%20set%20out%20in%20the%20International%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20Private%20Security%20Service%20Providers,%20the%20use%20of%20security%20personnel%20can%20also%20have%20negative%20impacts%20on%20local%20populations%20and%20on%20the%20upholding%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Office%20of%20the%20High%20Commissioner,%20&lsquo;human%20rights%20education%20constitutes%20an%20essential%20contribution%20to%20the%20long-term%20prevention%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%20and%20represents%20an%20important%20investment%20in%20the%20endeavor%20to%20achieve%20a%20just%20society%20in%20which%20all%20human%20rights%20of%20all%20persons%20are%20valued%20and%20respected.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3ETraining%20security%20personnel%20in%20human%20rights%20can%20therefore%20help%20to%20ensure%20their%20appropriate%20conduct%20towards%20third%20parties,%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20use%20of%20force.%20This%20disclosure%20indicates%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20security%20force%20that%20can%20reasonably%20be%20assumed%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20an%20organization&rsquo;s%20expectations%20of%20human%20rights%20performance.%20Information%20provided%20under%20this%20disclosure%20can%20demonstrate%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20management%20systems%20pertaining%20to%20human%20rights%20are%20implemented.%3C/div%3E",
